888
00:37:29,300 --> 00:37:30,780
<font size="20">Is that Miss Hua called Hua Zhi?</font>

889
00:37:31,740 --> 00:37:32,300
<font size="20">Yes.</font>

890
00:37:33,180 --> 00:37:34,100
<font size="20">So it is her.</font>

891
00:37:35,620 --> 00:37:36,140
<font size="20">Let her go.</font>

892
00:37:36,500 --> 00:37:37,220
<font size="20">Yes.</font>

893
00:37:56,420 --> 00:37:57,060
<font size="20">Commander,</font>

894
