<font size="20">I thought Hua...</font>

988
00:42:06,180 --> 00:42:07,420
<font size="20">that you must be anxious,</font>

989
00:42:07,500 --> 00:42:08,220
<font size="20">so I came.</font>

990
00:42:09,500 --> 00:42:11,340
<font size="20">Chen Zhi came to rob us.</font>

991
00:42:11,460 --> 00:42:12,260
