1003
00:42:28,860 --> 00:42:29,780
<font size="20">They might be able to speak</font>

1004
00:42:29,780 --> 00:42:30,220
<font size="20">with the Seven-Star Bureau.</font>

1005
00:42:30,580 --> 00:42:31,060
<font size="20">The pressing matter at hand</font>

1006
00:42:31,060 --> 00:42:31,900
<font size="20">is to bring Hua Zhi back.</font>

1007
00:42:33,220 --> 00:42:34,260
<font size="20">By the way, Madam Xia,</font>

1008
00:42:34,660 --> 00:42:35,620
<font size="20">I don't have any cash on me
at the moment.</font>

1009
00:42:35,700 --> 00:42:36,540
<font size="20">Once I have raised the money,</font>

1010
00:42:36,540 --> 00:42:37,380
<font size="20">I will immediately send it to you.</font>

1011
00:42:38,460 --> 00:42:39,100
<font size="20">Farewell.</font>

