<font size="20">get him in the end.</font>

1024
00:43:09,100 --> 00:43:10,460
<font size="20">Don't you know our situation?</font>

1025
00:43:10,540 --> 00:43:11,780
<font size="20">Isn't it shameful enough already?</font>

1026
00:43:13,860 --> 00:43:15,140
<font size="20">We are now at the end of our tether.</font>

1027
00:43:15,420 --> 00:43:16,180
<font size="20">He is our</font>

1028
00:43:16,180 --> 00:43:17,140
<font size="20">only hope.</font>

